[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     39[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Because this recipe is the single highest-stakes recipe in chapter 12 (real-time clinical deterioration detection, alert fatigue is the dominant operational failure mode, and the FDA SaMD boundary is genuinely close enough to graze), the panel is also recording substantive forward-looking expert commentary so the TechWriter has the full benchmark on the first pass. This is the same approach the panel took for recipe 12.6 and the chapter pattern that emerged in 12.4 and 12.5.
