[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    161[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Clinical scoring frameworks**
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    162[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    163[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - NEWS2: Royal College of Physicians, "National Early Warning Score (NEWS) 2," 2017 (UK NHS standard for adult ward patients).
